Currency :	

- Coins on Earth
- Ruthenium (RU) kicks in on Titan. 
- Used to buy upgrades for gear, lethals, non lethals, weapons. From vendors.
-cannot buy Gems- 


			
Gems:  
          	Weapon Enhancers: 
-Colored Aura on weapon
     			-Stat Boost, Predetermined based on Gem used


	 	Colors:
Top Tier:   	Colorless - multiple stat boost
			Diamond  - 
			Ruby        -
			Emerald   -
	Low Tier:	Gold         -

Find in the wild only.

