Alien Hierarchy:

Species: Wraith
          Queen - Master of All, Can summon any aliens to help her besides oracles
	Oracles - Gun and Magic
	Archon’s - Magic based.
	Dravec’s - Chameleon ( Predator Style, Active Camo)
	Harpy’s - Flying Aliens
	Guardians - Gun Based
	Grunts - Hands on, no weapons	
	
               

Oracle Names:
		Pustota: Void Oracle       (Unholy in Russian) (Earth)
Salnos:  Ice Oracle         (Frost in Lithuanian) (Titan)
Gehénnam : Fire Oracle (Hellfire in Latin)       (Hyperion)
Königin: Queen Oracle   (Queen in German)(Nexus)
         		Titus:  Unholy Oracle          (King’s right hand Man)
Borivoj: King Oracle       (King in Czech)




	
